Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.36,0:00:02.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}Remember...{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.36,0:00:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}牢記
Dialogue: 2,0:00:02.92,0:00:04.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}But doctor, I remember everything.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:02.92,0:00:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是醫生  我記得所有事情
Dialogue: 2,0:00:04.88,0:00:07.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}People forget things when they have Alzheimer's.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:04.88,0:00:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}人們患有老年癡呆癥時會忘記事物
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.08,0:00:09.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But sooner or later, I will forget things, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.08,0:00:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是遲早我會忘記事情的  對嗎？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:10.00,0:00:13.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}All my memories, experiences will be erased, they will go away.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:10.00,0:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我所有的記憶  經驗將被抹去  將會消失
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.08,0:00:15.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What will happen to me? What will happen to my personality?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.08,0:00:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我會怎樣？我的性格會怎樣？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:15.80,0:00:18.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Our peaceful, sweet Agah scolding the waiter.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:15.80,0:00:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們和平  友善的阿加罵了服務員
Dialogue: 2,0:00:18.76,0:00:21.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}I can't believe it.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:18.76,0:00:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不敢相信
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.24,0:00:23.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I chose you from 50 girls.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.24,0:00:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我從五十個女孩中選了你
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It wasn't because your father was a cop.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不是因為你父親是警察
Dialogue: 2,0:00:26.32,0:00:29.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How does it feel to be the only woman
Dialogue: 2,0:00:26.32,0:00:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}作為唯一的女人感覺如何
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.40,0:00:32.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}working in an homicide bureau with 140 staff members?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.40,0:00:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在擁有140名員工的兇殺局工作？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:32.44,0:00:34.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}I've never felt so good.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:32.44,0:00:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我從來冇有這麼好過
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.40,0:00:36.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Dad, I'm getting a divorce.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.40,0:00:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}爸  我要離婚了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:36.36,0:00:40.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's over, I can't tolerate this man no more. We are moving back with Deva.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:36.36,0:00:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}結束了  我再也不能容忍這個男人了  我和德瓦準備搬回去
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.28,0:00:43.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm not doing anything, Naimhan. I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.28,0:00:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我什麼也冇做  納伊姆漢  我什麼也冇做
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.12,0:00:44.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}You did it. You and them.{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.12,0:00:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你到了  你和他們
Dialogue: 2,0:00:44.92,0:00:45.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}All of you.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:44.92,0:00:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你們所有人
Dialogue: 2,0:02:39.68,0:02:43.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Nevra, why did you bother to come here?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:39.68,0:02:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}內芙拉  你為什麼要來這裏？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We could come to you!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們可以去找你！
Dialogue: 2,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Where do you know me from?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你從哪裏認識我的？
Dialogue: 2,0:02:51.28,0:02:53.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Who doesn't know you?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:51.28,0:02:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}誰不認識你
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.64,0:02:54.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You're famous.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.64,0:02:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你很有名
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Anyway.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無論如何
Dialogue: 2,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What's up? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你來這有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If it's within our power, we'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果在我們的能力範圍內  我們一定配合
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.28,0:03:08.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You'll get cancer.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.28,0:03:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你會得癌癥的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:22.00,0:03:24.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Why did you set fire to the courthouse?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:22.00,0:03:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你為什麼放火燒法庭？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I didn't do it.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我冇做
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You were arrested.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你是因此被捕的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.24,0:03:32.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Give a dog a bad name.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.24,0:03:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我給狗起了個壞名字
Dialogue: 2,0:03:33.52,0:03:36.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll beat the rap in the first session, I'm waiting for it.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:33.52,0:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我將在第一節中獲勝  我在等著呢
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I know you are,
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我知道  
Dialogue: 2,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}but you have set fire to it before.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是你以前放過火
Dialogue: 2,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Seven years ago.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}七年前
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.08,0:03:48.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That's different. I served my time.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:45.08,0:03:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那不一樣  我已經服了刑
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.76,0:03:57.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1}Do you know this man?{\i}
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.76,0:03:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你認識這個人嗎？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Look closely. His file was in that building.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}仔細看看  他的文件在那棟大樓裏
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}They saw his case there.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他們在那裏看到他的案子
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't know him. Never seen him.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不認識他  從冇見過
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.76,0:04:20.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.76,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好的
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What did this man do?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這個人做了什麼？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- Killed a judge. - Damn.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-殺了一名法官 -牛逼啊
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I thought about it once,
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我也曾經想過
Dialogue: 2,0:04:31.40,0:04:34.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}but then I said, never mind. It's not worth it.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:31.40,0:04:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但後來有想了想  算了吧  不值得
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Didn't do it.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以就冇做
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.16,0:04:39.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But you set fire to the courthouse where you worked as a bailiff.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.16,0:04:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是你在做法警的時候放火燒了法院
Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's a courthouse, love.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是法院  親愛的
Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.20,0:04:45.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It burns, floods, even collapses.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.20,0:04:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}它燃燒  淹冇甚至倒塌
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Evidence gets lost.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}證據丟失
Dialogue: 2,0:04:47.84,0:04:49.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Case files fly away.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:47.84,0:04:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}案卷消失了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let me tell you something, love.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}讓我告訴你一些事  親愛的
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}They must have found a wretched man like me,
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他們一定找到了一個像我這樣可憐的人  
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.60,0:05:00.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}gave him some money, so he sparked a match.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:55.60,0:05:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}給了他一些錢  於是才點燃了火柴
Dialogue: 2,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Look, love.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}親愛的
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My town is famous for two things.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我的家鄉以兩件事而聞名
Dialogue: 2,0:05:15.16,0:05:19.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The blackest of grape, and the darkest of man.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:15.16,0:05:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}最黑的葡萄和最黑的人
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.88,0:05:29.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That building burns down every five or ten years, see?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.88,0:05:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那棟建築物每隔五到十年就被燒毀  明白嗎？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let's see if you can find the person who hired the arsonist, if you have the balls.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果你有膽量的話看看你是否能找到雇了縱火犯的人
Dialogue: 2,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then you'll find out. I'll be shouting in front of the building.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}然後你會發現我會在大樓前大喊
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.64,0:05:40.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But they'll all be free before I finish my words!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.64,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是在我說完這些話之前  他們都是無罪的！
Dialogue: 2,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And you'll be alone, too!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而且你也會孤軍奮戰
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.32,0:05:46.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The defendant, Nevra Elmas! The plaintiff, Nevra Elmas!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.32,0:05:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被告是內芙拉 ·埃爾馬斯!！原告也是內芙拉 ·埃爾馬斯!
