Dialogue: 2,0:45:35.36,0:45:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果它能運行了呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:45:36.92,0:45:38.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What if it comes down?
Dialogue: 2,0:45:36.92,0:45:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果降下來會怎樣？
Dialogue: 2,0:45:40.20,0:45:41.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:45:40.20,0:45:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那樣的話……
Dialogue: 2,0:45:42.52,0:45:43.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then...
Dialogue: 2,0:45:42.52,0:45:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那麼……
