Dialogue: 2,0:45:45.08,0:45:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我就要做一些我不喜歡做的事情了
Dialogue: 2,0:45:48.12,0:45:51.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}- I'll have to kill you. - Ah, man!
Dialogue: 2,0:45:48.12,0:45:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}-我得殺了你 -啊  天啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:45:51.36,0:45:52.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Help!
Dialogue: 2,0:45:51.36,0:45:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}救命！
